<div class="wrapper wrapper_padding clearfix">
    <div class="col-1 about homepage_content">
      <h2>About</h2>
      <hr />
      <p>An Okie from Muskogee who now calls Edmond home. I work full time as a Web Designer and Front-End Developer for LifeChurch.tv. I have been building websites for the past 5 years and love every minute of it. Passionate about Jesus and his Church, husband to my beautiful bride, Brea, father to, Tenley-Kate and Callaway, and a sucker for a good cup of coffee. Be blessed!</p>
      <!-- <p><img src="https://avatars1.githubusercontent.com/u/5542815?v=3&s=460" class="profile_img" /></p> -->
    </div>
    <div class="col-2 homepage_content">
      <h2>Stuff I've Written</h2>
      <hr />
      <% @posts.each do |post| %>
            <h3><a href="#"><%= link_to post.title, post %></a></h3>
            <p class="date"><%= post.created_at.strftime("%A, %b %d") %></p>
      <% end %>
    </div>
    <div class="col-3 homepage_content">
      <h2>Stuff I've Built</h2>
      <hr />
      <% @projects.each do |project| %>
            <h3><a href="#"><%= link_to project.title, project %></a></h3>
            <p class="date"><%= project.created_at.strftime("%A, %b %d") %></p>
      <% end %>
    </div>
  </div>